{"tid":2515623,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【Backup】 不如試下咁樣Backup 啲片","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:11:24.000Z","uid":296431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed50c3cc74a5f99ee0b97e63a05a35737ed434a","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"利申，純學術討論<br />\n<br />\n現時Backup 有兩大問題：<br />\n- Backup 進度混亂<br />\n- Backup 過於集中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以裝咗IPFS 先<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/ipfs/ipfs-desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fipfs%2Fipfs-desktop&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=186520f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/ipfs/ipfs-desktop</a><br />\n<br />\nQuick-install shortcuts <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後根據呢個list，自行backup 啲片，建議逐個系列咁下載，然後分類<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit#gid=1552175605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k%2Fedit%23gid%3D1552175605&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=eb0c85f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1JPyevWnxvoq_xzY4ptOgaTaTYSLE9oMva66kxm66K0k/edit#gid=1552175605</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分類之後，就可以放上IPFS Desktop （教學)<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/544880604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F544880604&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=aac1cd17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/544880604</a><br />\n<br />\n之後如果你想Share 俾人哋，就咁Copy IPFS 條LINK 就得，人地就可以睇到,下載埋都得<br />\n<br />\n例子 ：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmZyjSUSgcHEokDUE6sAoj5bsb3RcrEoYV9zn4FF59N3Nz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fipfs.io%2Fipfs%2FQmZyjSUSgcHEokDUE6sAoj5bsb3RcrEoYV9zn4FF59N3Nz&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=b3f0d822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmZyjSUSgcHEokDUE6sAoj5bsb3RcrEoYV9zn4FF59N3Nz</a><br />\n<br />\nPS: 希望整到個IPFS LINK LIST ，之後大家就咁用就得 <br />\n<br />\n有咩唔明可以問，盡量回答"},{"pid":"30f2b4bbc7ffe60526d15c1c6d83ed1c244016a1","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:19:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ac95e0c1daff22b32b8acff73a67c9bdba85c64","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeHABi3msU5HmpRtb13S6yoQftymirmJB3Fh1xAofWJBz?filename=gEFLLgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEFLLgx.png&h=a1aca3c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就咁下載，然後Next Next 就裝到"},{"pid":"8c79ceb4bcea2ad40be1f85803256ed8a6b64c4f","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"講返可以點解決問題<br />\n<br />\n進度混亂<br />\n- Backup 可以分系列咁去做，例如鏗鏘集, 香港歷史系列 IV，然後每人負責backup 幾個系列"},{"pid":"979650cd1d56be7ac49bda75141c9c4dc54ee771","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNeeyi2nU3geWFrtjsGoAbt4h2ndhvXZfD2ya9fuqE7rg?filename=9ndQWx3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ndQWx3.png&h=50232c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊IPFS Backup <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c83ba9ad855034bf3936d7d8564eb548c1fe64","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/544880604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F544880604&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=aac1cd17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/544880604</a><br />\n點樣upload 啲片上IPFS"},{"pid":"c8f3b65f8e266522601c57a3cc5bacba41a9dba7","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Collection 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fipfs.io%2Fipfs%2FQmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a6205a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq</a>"},{"pid":"1fca36dc913c0b73afc7b7908a0a1bcd3d8c1685","tid":2515623,"uid":388494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"71dad0891702f7c55baf7d53cece9ed656f82111","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fca36dc913c0b73afc7b7908a0a1bcd3d8c1685","tid":2515623,"uid":388494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"推一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"c8f3b65f8e266522601c57a3cc5bacba41a9dba7","tid":2515623,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:18:07.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong Collection 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fipfs.io%2Fipfs%2FQmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a6205a4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmTdj8VjRdUPLoTafEKFmjQrBugyffMbiytCGmLSJJDoJq</a>"}}